  "id": "RAW_0bfe2c51",
  "title": "英伟达的疯狂账本：一边收割巨头，一边「包养」OpenAI",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652650104&idx=2&sn=4f3e380cf49e76646e2d683cb81eb42b",
  "date": "2025-11-30 05:30:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165280\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhaCjYdTHYeYK8J54IKgr84aTnEdia0QpwMJDcZ0lJATGllN5RmkkYkKA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c055bb6a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhaCjYdTHYeYK8J54IKgr84aTnEdia0QpwMJDcZ0lJATGllN5RmkkYkKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">ChatGPT涨价、免费额度缩水，骂归骂，很多人还是没搞懂：到底谁在拿走我们的钱？其实，涨价的真正推手不是OpenAI，而是用GPU锁住AI底价的英伟达。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">ChatGPT涨价的讨论又冲上了首页。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Plus到手价从20美元涨到22美元、美区Team从25美元涨到30美元，Claude在20美元的Pro之外，又新增了30美元的Team档和Max档，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">有人骂贵，有人觉得情有可原，更多人开始意识到：AI正在进入一个「越用越贵」的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">可顺着成本链条往下看，会发现涨价的真正推手既不是OpenAI，也不是Anthropic，而是Nvidia。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">所有AI公司都在为它的GPU付账，用户最终为这条链买单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">涨价的起点：算力被Nvidia推上去了</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">外界把涨价的矛头指向OpenAI，可真正把整个行业往贵的方向推的，是算力成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">把「算力」 这两个字拆开看，其实就是三个字：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">英伟达</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">据The Information报道，这一轮涨价背后，是Nvidia的现金流在过去两年里出现了几乎前所未有的爆炸性增长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">截至2023年1月，它的自由现金流只有38亿美元；到了明年，预计会飙到965亿美元，三年复合增长率高达194%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">短短四年，它的自由现金流放大了二十多倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这种增速，在1990年以来的大型科技公司里都极为罕见，能勉强靠近的只有iPod刚问世那几年的苹果，但幅度仍不及Nvidia。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"423\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505165281\" data-ratio=\"0.7535483870967742\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"775\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=846657c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhYho49JqRGeQbmbbJDwlxeTPC8pibuNMib6xY8RPMzq0ib876MwbXRYruA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Nvidia的自由现金流在四年内接近百倍暴涨，远超Meta与Apple在各自巅峰时期的增速</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这种增长不是凭空出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">2023年ChatGPT爆火后，全球科技公司一齐冲向Nvidia订购AI芯片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Google、Meta、微软、亚马逊在AI上的投入全面上升，它们疯狂扩建数据中心、抢购GPU，Nvidia直接变成算力时代的核心供货商。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"409\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505165282\" data-ratio=\"0.7072243346007605\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"789\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c974aabd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhybdJoJiaL8QJZrj6baiabhZY7BbiczEiaFVqjI0PjvUTuwE64UEQqpzaww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">ChatGPT点燃AI浪潮后，Nvidia的营收与自由现金流在四年内直线上冲，远超资本开支的增幅，形成史无前例的「现金喷泉」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">The Information在报道里提到一个关键趋势：谷歌、Meta、亚马逊和微软因为大规模购入Nvidia的GPU，自身的自由现金流被明显压低，可用来维持「免费服务」的现金池变小了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">我们看到的那些「免费额度减少」「会员涨价」「高级模型限流」，都和这一点息息相关。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">巨头为了继续做AI，只能把算力成本摊给用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">与此同时，Nvidia的的现金储备也在持续膨胀。从2023年初大约130亿美元，上升到今年10月底的600亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">分析师预计，从现在到2030年，Nvidia累计会创造接近8500亿美元自由现金流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"418\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"894\" data-imgfileid=\"505165277\" data-ratio=\"0.7443796835970025\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1201\" data-width=\"1201\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dc8d66c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhI9DA1WgrcfibFxHgmHhr2FB3lqaYZBzZrbuUCdfmwmXUPF50Jr10yJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">分析师预计Nvidia在2027—2030年的自由现金流将持续走高，到2030年逼近3000亿美元</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这一总量，被认为已经明显高于分析师对Google、亚马逊、Meta、微软同一时期自由现金流的预期，也高于苹果被预计产生的自由现金流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">现金被掏空：巨头把成本转嫁给用户</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">当Nvidia的现金曲线开始向上「跳档」时，产业链的另一边已经有些吃不消了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Google、Meta、微软、亚马逊这几家最能赚钱的公司，过去两年都在加速扩建AI计算集群。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">它们的资本开支成倍增长，而自由现金流却被显著压缩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">也就是说，它们花的钱比以前多，手里能自由支配的现金却比以前少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这个变化直接影响了整个AI服务的收费方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">在此之前，巨头还能靠广告、云服务、硬件补贴用户，让产品保持免费。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">但当数据中心不断扩建、GPU价格居高不下，它们第一次发现：AI服务不能再无限免费了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">于是我们就看到：强模型被放进更贵的付费层，免费额度开始收紧，订阅费一点点往上挪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这些公司的商业模式没什么本质变化，它们只是被迫承认一个现实——算力成本持续上升，如果价格不调整，就只能长期亏钱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">更关键的是，Nvidia不只卖芯片，它还在投资、扶持整条下游链条。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Anthropic、CoreWeave、Lambda这些云和模型公司，都在它的生态之内；最近它和微软一起宣布，未来几年最高会向Anthropic投入150亿美元，其中Nvidia自己的部分最高可达100亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhSibsJZT0qcaxuzxO66icS3lhYnoSKYHe7C0AefNQqEicTwQ6hmqCUCbqw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"10.711743772241993\" data-cropx2=\"1204\" data-cropy2=\"505.5943060498221\" data-height=\"505\" data-imgfileid=\"505165275\" data-ratio=\"0.42294807370184256\" style=\"width:557px;height:236px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1194\" data-width=\"1204\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=82cf5ca6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhrMFCJ3bcTVaiapK4T976upq0P4KCY406Nf8B0cP9CCn2yDTqAY3F4XQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">有这么多的需求，GPU的价格就很难往下走。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">巨头买GPU的成本压不下来，AI产品自然也不可能回到过去那种「想用多少用多少」的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">供应商变金主：Nvidia把AI底价锁死了</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">所以问题已经不再是「为什么涨价」，而是：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">为什么未来几年</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">的价格都很难降下来。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">原因不是市场竞争不够，而是Nvidia已经在用另一套逻辑，把整个AI行业的基础结构提前固定住了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">The Information提到Nvidia的几个关键操作：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">向Anthropic投入100亿美元</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">与OpenAI商谈规模高达千亿美元级别的长期合作；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">支持CoreWeave、Lambda等云厂商扩建算力</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">替一家云公司担保数据中心租约，换取未来的GPU订单</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"608\" data-imgfileid=\"505165276\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41bf0a8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbh3ic4IV3FSIjHUSO36M4Rkt5W44LrdBnanQcLxtRgkMbekicvxzOc9m8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这些看起来像是财务投资，实质是一种「提前绑定」：谁来买卡、买多久、买多少，Nvidia都提前把关系锁好了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">被绑定的公司规模越大，算力需求越高，Nvidia的收益也越高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">再叠加CUDA的生态壁垒、台积电的产能限制、替代方案的落地周期这些现实因素，很容易得出的结论：行业短期内根本离不开Nvidia。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"280\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1104\" data-imgfileid=\"505165279\" data-ratio=\"0.4981949458483754\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"2216\" data-width=\"2216\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24e98c31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbh10UF6E5VYz3elx3touzTTOKicUBugsfNWONly8ak5ibHVooziaGkCazKQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">一旦离不开，成本就不会降。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">就算巨头有心拉低价格，也会被供不应求的 GPU 和已经锁定的产能限制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">对用户来说，这意味着AI会越来越强，但「免费时代」几乎不可能回来了；更好的模型，会停在更高的价格层；按量计费会变成常态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">整个行业已经切到一条不会轻易反转的轨道上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">成本不会突然降低，价格自然也不会。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">过去一年，我们习惯把AI看作一种「能力爆发」，但Nvidia的曲线提醒我们，背后还有一场静悄悄的基础设施重构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"294\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"426\" data-imgfileid=\"505165278\" data-ratio=\"0.5239852398523985\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"813\" data-width=\"813\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=198a7bbd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibIPlzoQwmKDwvI12LqSbhF2ZdtXndZT64DNOsYmwdbhjFMBQ5rhC1icw7zJmxVicuc7x6AWicsM18w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">当算力被锁定，当供应链被提前写入未来，当整个行业都围着同一个底层旋转——价格就不再只是市场行为，而是一种结构性趋势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">你的时间、你的技能、你的效率，也会在这条曲线里被重新定价。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">成本会上升，但它推动的，未必只有负担，也可能是价值的整体抬升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.theinformation.com/articles/nvidias-mushrooming-cash-pile-spotlights-spending-choices?rc=epv9gi\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theinformation.com/articles/nvidias-mushrooming-cash-pile-spotlights-spending-choices?rc=epv9gi</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章揭示英伟达通过其在 GPU 市场的绝对主导地位及对 AI 公司的战略投资，成为 AI 服务成本上涨的真正推手，锁定行业基础价格并终结 AI 免费时代。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章揭示英伟达通过其在 GPU 市场的绝对主导地位及对 AI 公司的战略投资，成为 AI 服务成本上涨的真正推手，锁定行业基础价格并终结 AI 免费时代。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了当前 AI 服务（如 ChatGPT）订阅费用上涨的深层原因，指出其并非主要由 OpenAI 或 Anthropic 驱动，而是源于英伟达在 AI 算力供应链中的核心主导地位。通过引用 The Information 的报道和财务数据，文章揭示了英伟达自由现金流的惊人增长，以及大型科技公司为获取 GPU 而大幅增加资本开支，从而被迫将算力成本转嫁给用户。更重要的是，英伟达不仅销售芯片，还通过对 Anthropic、CoreWeave、Lambda 等下游公司的巨额投资和长期合作谈判，提前绑定了算力需求和供应，结合 CUDA 生态壁垒和台积电产能限制，形成了对 AI 行业底层成本结构的牢固锁定。这预示着 AI 服务短期内价格难以下降，并将进入一个“越用越贵”的时代，终结了 AI 的“免费时代”，推动了基础设施的重构和价值的整体抬升。",
